import React from 'react'
import {Container ,Title,Wraper ,Img ,Item} from './style'
import Carousel from 'react-elastic-carousel'
const Customer = () => {
    return (
      <Container>
          <Title>What Our Customer Says</Title>

           <Wraper>
                  <Carousel itemsToShow={1} >
                     <Item>1</Item>
                     <Item>2</Item>
                     <Item>3</Item>
                     <Item>4</Item>
                 </Carousel>
           </Wraper>
      </Container>
    )
}

export default Customer
